{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"37d8d884-e103-4a55-8bda-117ddc4a3675","content":"No existing files found. Here's how to convert your page to compiled bindings and catch errors at build time:\n\n**Add `x:DataType` to your ContentPage root element:**\n\n```xml\n<ContentPage xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n             xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n             xmlns:vm=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.ViewModels\"\n             x:Class=\"YourApp.Views.SettingsPage\"\n             x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\">\n\n    <VerticalStackLayout>\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding Theme}\" />\n        <Switch IsToggled=\"{Binding NotificationsEnabled}\" />\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding FontSize}\" />\n    </VerticalStackLayout>\n</ContentPage>\n```\n\n**Key changes:**\n1. Added `xmlns:vm` pointing to your ViewModel namespace.\n2. Added `x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"` on the `<ContentPage>` — this enables compiled bindings for the entire page.\n\n**How to catch binding errors at build time:**\n\nWith `x:DataType` set, the XAML compiler validates bindings against the declared type. If you typo a property (e.g., `{Binding Themee}`), you'll get a **build error** like:\n\n```\nXC0045: Binding: Property \"Themee\" not found on \"SettingsViewModel\"\n```\n\nNo extra configuration needed — `x:DataType` alone enables this. To ensure it's active project-wide, confirm your `.csproj` does **not** disable XAML compilation:\n\n```xml\n<!-- This should NOT be in your .csproj (it disables compiled bindings): -->\n<!-- <MauiXamlCInterpretation>true</MauiXamlCInterpretation> -->\n```\n\n**Tips:**\n- If a sub-element binds to a different type (e.g., inside a `DataTemplate`), add a local `x:DataType` on that element.\n- To opt out for one binding (e.g., a relative source), use `x:DataType=\"\"` on that element to suppress the check.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"1888f855-3c02-4e39-b186-04d4cb6a8a77","outputTokens":529,"requestId":"5032:8A8EB:1AFE94A:1DFD007:69FA8FAD"},"id":"805b0035-6734-40e5-be2d-c9857b90bc2d","timestamp":"2026-05-06T00:47:52.721Z","parentId":"f73f394f-1d80-4844-a697-376fe280874f"}
